  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'What can I get you? Supply stocks are low, but we''re managing.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1430870eaeabf6d4b92a3358307ba4e3, type: 3}
    nextOption: What do you have in stock?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Less than yesterday, more than tomorrow. The usual situation.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2d505a5fee8475c4190e378085575626, type: 3}
    nextOption: Is there anything I should know?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Keep your coin where you can reach it fast. Prices change when the fighting gets close.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 371cb9231a1d08b4980f3f1fee4f4c1b, type: 3}
    nextOption: Noted. Let me see what you have.
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Take your time. I''m not going anywhere — someone has to stay and sell things when everyone else is retreating.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4c4ce7bf75a9c5d40ba3b46268e9651c, type: 3}
    nextOption: Smart business.
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Smart survival. There''s a difference. Now — anything else, or shall we trade?'
